high_descs: Turn right, go to the sink on the right.
Take the knife to the right of the sink.
Turn right, go to the microwave at the end of the counter.
Cut the potato in the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave.
Take a slice of potato from the microwave.
Go to the refrigerator on the right.
Put the slice of potato in the middle rack of the refrigerator. Close the refrigerator. Take the slice of potato out of the microwave.
Go to the microwave to the left.
Put the slice of potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of potato in the microwave.

high_descs: turn right, go to just before the sink, and turn right again
take the knife
turn right and head to the microwave
open the microwave
put the knife in the microwave
use the knife in the microwave to slice the potato in the microwave, take the potato slice, and close the microwave door
turn right and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator, put the potato slice in the refrigerator, wait 7 seconds, open the refrigerator, and take the potato slice out.
go back to the microwave
open the microwave, put the slice of potato in the microwave, and close the door
anns.task_desc: place a slightly chilled potato slice in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and move across the room to the sink that will be on the left.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn and move to the microwave.
Open the microwave door in front you.
Slice the potato that is in the microwave.
Take a slice of potato.  Close the door.
Turn to the left and stop at the fridge.
Open the door.  Place the potato on the shelf.  Close the door and allow potato to cool.
Open the door and take the potato out.  Move back to the microwave.
Open the door.  Place the potato inside, close the door,  and reheat the potato.
anns.task_desc: Preparing a potato to eat, store, & reheat.
